    <li>
      <p>
        In this tutorial, that builds on the first part of the Cookbook tutorial, we will 
        explain how CSV (Comma Separated Value) files can be used to: view data, upload new data
        and create new models for a project.
      </p>
      <p>
        So lets get started and go to the "Cookbook" project.  Just click the Cookbook link on
        the sidebar.
      </p>
      <p ><img width=600 height=400
      id="Picture 1" alt="homepage" class="csv_tutorial_image" 
